= Introduction =
Browser Choice is a user-friendly installer dialog for choosing a web browser on {{project_name_short}}. It provides a convenient way to install or remove browsers without forcing a single default choice for all users.

For background and technical details (design, plugin system, inclusion criteria), see [[Dev/browser-choice|Browser Choice (<u>dev</u>elopers)]]. For broader context on default browser considerations, see [[Dev/Default_Browser|Default Browser (dev)]].

